quran[9{c,v,t}:
47,30,hum chahain to inhen tum ko aankhon se dikha den aur unn ke cheharon se tum un ko pehchan lau magar un ke andaaz kalaam se to tum un ko jaan hi lau ge Allah tum sab ke aamaal se khoob waaqif hai
47,31,hum zaroor tum logon ko azmaish mein dalain ge taakay tumahray halaat ki jaanch karen aur dekh len ke tum mein Mujahid aur saabit qadam kon hain
47,32,"jin logon ne kufar kya aur Allah ki raah se roka aur rasool se jhagra kya jabkay un par raah raast wazeh ho chuki thi, Dur haqeeqat woh Allah ka koi nuqsaan bhi nahi kar satke, balkay Allah hi un ka sab kya karaya ghaarat kar day ga"
47,33,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, tum Allah ki itaat karo aur rasool ki itaat karo aur apne aamaal ko barbaad nah kar lau"
47,34,kufar karne walon aur raah khuda se roknay walon aur martay dam taq kufar par jamay rehne walon ko to Allah hargiz maaf nah kere ga
47,35,pas tum boday nah bano aur sulah ki darkhwast nah karo tum hi ghalib rehne walay ho Allah tumahray sath hai aur tumahray aamaal ko woh hargiz zaya nah kere ga
47,36,yeh duniya ki zindagi to aik khail aur tamasha hai agar tum imaan rakho aur taqwa ki rawish par chaltay raho to Allah tumahray ajar tum ko day ga aur woh tumahray maal tum se nah mangay ga
47,37,agar kahin woh tumahray maal tum se maang le aur sab ke sab tum se talab kar le to tum bukhal karo ge aur woh tumahray khout ubhaar laaye ga
47,38,"dekho, tum logon ko dawat di ja rahi hai ke Allah ki raah mein maal kharch karo iss par tum mein se kuch log hain jo bukhal kar rahay hain, halaank jo bukhal karta hai woh Dur haqeeqat apne aap hi se bukhal kar raha hai Allah to ghanni hai, tum hi is ke mohtaaj ho agar tum mun morron ge to Allah tumhari jagah kisi aur qoum ko le aeye ga aur woh tum jaisay nah hon ge"
